
The application has two main forms:

1) A user interface is hosted on our site with the https://www.tradingview.com/widget/ widget. User can interact directly with this widget on the site.

2) The application has a curl call feature where a user can provide a stock ticker and the response will display the most recent 10K filing section 1A 'Risk Factors' from the company and a NLTK sentiment analysis performed on this section.  We are utilizing a free service offered by the SEC EDGAR database, which is limitied to 100 quieres.  Our usage can be seen here: https://sec-api.io/profile
